{"tid":1682830,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple Watch 4用電勁快","createTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:25.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-30T10:55:11.000Z","uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"738116d04b0070bde2f9e6d933103ba56a4accf2","tid":1682830,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:25.000Z","msg":"明明之前由早戴到晚，都仲有成70幾%電，<br />\n但呢幾日用電勁快，去到黃昏時已跌到10%<br />\n<br />\n今日突登mark住個電量，<br />\n朝早7:30開機時有100%，<br />\n上午時耗電已經好快，平均每小時跌4%<br />\n<br />\n去到14:00後仲離譜，急跌到17:30時得返10%<br />\n<br />\n粗畫圖如下：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rfEJg5U.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrfEJg5U.png&h=5b482810&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我已熄晒對講機果d功能，<br />\n今日基本上只用隻錶黎睇時間 + 睇whatsapp message，<br />\n有冇巴打知點解會咁？<br />\n有冇巴打可以救救小弟隻錶？<br />\nThx bros<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b759737f1afd48ad42184b75f97993c16ffd029","tid":1682830,"uid":1477,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:50:51.000Z","msg":"其實要達成目標<br />\n不外乎都係開源節流<br />\n開源，好簡單，姐係要令對方加入己方陣營<br />\n都係教育佢地民主是個好東西<br />\n<br />\n但有d 長者唔會明<br />\n咁呢個時候就要節流<br />\n佢地班口撐支那唔緊要<br />\n肉體懼怕支那先最實際<br />\n正如有d 人口裡反美心，身體卻去食元氣<br />\n呢d 真係唔太實際囉<br />\n<br />\n為左節流<br />\n大家快d share 文宣比長者睇<br />\n支那嘅恐怖真係隨時影響到香港<br />\n到時棺材都無埋就好笑<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E3ADQhD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE3ADQhD.jpg&h=fbfa3f8a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7L003CF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7L003CF.jpg&h=0bf8c277&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1e0aa32779116934921936e71ca111e06ab19a06","tid":1682830,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"我差一次用2-3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbd6d5a1db6602e2ad95091f77be5b08c9da5201","tid":1682830,"uid":66365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0aa32779116934921936e71ca111e06ab19a06","tid":1682830,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"我差一次用2-3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:53:39.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb14e764123032919f138552b1439f60a03bc819","tid":1682830,"uid":171149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0aa32779116934921936e71ca111e06ab19a06","tid":1682830,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"我差一次用2-3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:53:50.000Z","msg":"Me too"},{"pid":"b62ca882ff6e956a5e5781fe1affb782ffac1e1c","tid":1682830,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0aa32779116934921936e71ca111e06ab19a06","tid":1682830,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:53:19.000Z","msg":"我差一次用2-3日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-30T09:59:15.000Z","msg":"我頭幾個月都係咁"},{"pid":"fd9bd185551f4a91a4f6d293b707ab4818192d45","tid":1682830,"uid":179007,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b62ca882ff6e956a5e5781fe1affb782ffac1e1c","tid":1682830,"uid":73910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e0aa32779116934921936e71ca111e06ab19a06","tid":16828